POWER TO THE PERSON 

Hopefully by this point you've found some batteries, and some means to charge them. The easiest way to supply power to a network is by connecting batteries to an Area Power Control unit. To provide the power you'll need for Smelting and bulk manufacturing however, you'll need something a little more convenient. The best way to handle this depends on your situation, but options include;
